<p><%= I18n.t("questions.about.this_is_a_web_app_created_for_people_with_juvenile_records_in_illinois", :default => "This is a web app created for people with juvenile records in Illinois.") %></p>

<p>A juvenile record is a barrier to employment and education. Luckily, juvenile records can be erased through the expungement process. However, while the majority of juvenile records can be erased, <a href="http://chiyouthjustice.wordpress.com/2013/02/04/cook-county-juvenile-expungement-numbers-vs-arrests/"><%= I18n.t("questions.about.few_people_apply_for_juvenile_expungement", :default => "few people apply for juvenile expungement") %></a>. This web app aims to clarify juvenile expungement, with the hope of more people getting their records erased!</p>

<p>The <a href="http://www.mikvachallenge.org/site/epage/146561_719.htm"><%= I18n.t("questions.about.idea_for_this_app", :default => "idea for this app") %></a> came from the awesome <a href="https://twitter.com/MCJJustice">Juvenile Justice Council</a> of the <a href="https://twitter.com/MikvaChallenge">Mikva Challenge</a></p>

